WEBVTT

00:00:50.780 --> 00:00:55.740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

00:00:56.820 --> 00:00:59.780
=Episode 22=
=The Memory Etched in the Heart=

00:01:01.060 --> 00:01:03.580
(Wishlist: Go camping with her;
Cook for her; Driver's license)

00:01:03.580 --> 00:01:04.920
(Watch the stars and the sunrise)

00:01:04.920 --> 00:01:07.250
(Buy her favorite books;
Visit Tianyi High School with her)

00:01:07.250 --> 00:01:09.620
(Give her pretty earrings;
Go to Happy Valley once)

00:01:09.620 --> 00:01:12.740
(Take a photo together;
Go on a day trip)

00:01:12.740 --> 00:01:15.580
(Get her snacks;
Buy her skincare)

00:01:15.580 --> 00:01:18.420
(Give her some money)

00:01:18.420 --> 00:01:22.940
(Stop her from
crossing her legs too casually)

00:01:22.940 --> 00:01:24.380
(Teach her how to do makeup)

00:01:24.380 --> 00:01:26.580
(Improve her spoken English;
Go to the beach)

00:01:27.580 --> 00:01:28.780
(Try an escape room together)

00:01:28.780 --> 00:01:30.760
(Take a portrait set with her;
Watch the sunset)

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:31.990
(Give her a bouquet of flowers)

00:01:31.990 --> 00:01:33.780
(Buy her a new phone;
Get her a car)

00:01:33.780 --> 00:01:35.780
(Bake pastries for her)

00:01:35.780 --> 00:01:37.780
(Swing on the playground with her)

00:01:37.780 --> 00:01:41.860
(Hold the most romantic
seaside wedding for her)

00:01:43.620 --> 00:01:46.140
(Hold the most romantic
seaside wedding for her)

00:01:46.490 --> 00:01:47.440
(Ding Daang,)

00:01:47.560 --> 00:01:49.280
(this is the last thing)

00:01:49.600 --> 00:01:51.120
(I can do for you.)

00:01:52.140 --> 00:01:55.160
♪You keep running through my mind♪

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:58.560
♪Nothing matters more than you♪

00:01:58.640 --> 00:01:59.840
♪Why?♪

00:02:00.150 --> 00:02:03.940
♪You walked out of my world♪

00:02:05.080 --> 00:02:06.000
Brother.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:06.840
Sister.

00:02:07.280 --> 00:02:08.120
Happy wedding.

00:02:12.840 --> 00:02:13.680
Thank you.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:15.600
Now, groom,

00:02:15.600 --> 00:02:17.560
please kiss the bride.

00:02:18.230 --> 00:02:20.630
♪That song keeps playing on repeat♪

00:02:21.190 --> 00:02:23.540
♪Feels like
everything has frozen in time♪

00:02:24.190 --> 00:02:29.390
♪Where our happy moments were buried♪

00:02:29.940 --> 00:02:32.820
♪I wonder what you're doing now♪

00:02:33.020 --> 00:02:35.810
♪Are you really happier than before?♪

00:02:37.670 --> 00:02:41.380
♪Living the life you always wanted♪

00:02:42.100 --> 00:02:44.420
♪The final note faded away♪

00:02:44.420 --> 00:02:47.220
♪Let it be.
Maybe I was just holding on too tight♪

00:02:47.220 --> 00:02:49.460
♪Roses are meant to bloom someday♪

00:02:49.720 --> 00:02:54.540
♪Look up, you'll see a sky full of stars♪

00:02:55.150 --> 00:02:58.230
♪You keep running through my mind♪

00:02:58.240 --> 00:03:01.180
♪Nothing matters more than you♪

00:03:01.710 --> 00:03:02.720
♪Why?♪

00:03:03.180 --> 00:03:06.940
♪You walked out of my world♪

00:03:07.270 --> 00:03:09.980
♪You are my only cure♪

00:03:10.260 --> 00:03:13.600
♪Can you give me one more hug?♪

00:03:15.230 --> 00:03:19.040
♪Did you hear me say please don't go♪

00:03:19.320 --> 00:03:22.000
♪Silently I pray for you♪

00:03:22.280 --> 00:03:25.320
♪Wishing you a better life than mine♪

00:03:27.120 --> 00:03:32.340
♪It no longer matters
if you're not by my side♪

00:03:37.240 --> 00:03:39.040
If one day you pass away,

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:40.720
where would you want to be laid to rest?

00:03:47.720 --> 00:03:49.240
Anywhere would be fine.

00:03:49.240 --> 00:03:50.640
As long as you're beside me.

00:04:11.880 --> 00:04:13.280
Look, that's beautiful.

00:04:14.960 --> 00:04:15.800
Maimai.

00:04:16.280 --> 00:04:17.460
Where do you want

00:04:17.460 --> 00:04:18.400
our wedding to be held?

00:04:21.100 --> 00:04:21.940
Anywhere's fine.

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:23.920
Except by the beach.

00:04:24.440 --> 00:04:26.200
I don't like doing
what everyone else does.

00:04:27.080 --> 00:04:27.920
Got it.

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:30.440
Do you really get it?

00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:31.440
Yes.

00:04:46.840 --> 00:04:47.680
Ding Daang.

00:04:49.840 --> 00:04:51.160
Remember when we eloped?

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:00.640
How about we...

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:02.400
doing it again?

00:05:04.280 --> 00:05:05.120
Right now?

00:05:25.460 --> 00:05:29.580
(Aiye Town)

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:40.440
Ding Daang.

00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:44.720
I remember.

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:49.200
You used to pick a random chair to sit in

00:05:49.200 --> 00:05:50.180
and secretly watching me.

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:53.360
I also remember,

00:05:54.440 --> 00:05:56.320
when you gave Miaomiao that red dress,

00:05:56.320 --> 00:05:58.080
she danced around with joy.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:05.240
More importantly,

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:07.560
I remember you,

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:09.400
Ding Daang.

00:06:14.360 --> 00:06:15.520
I'm Yu Kun.

00:06:18.600 --> 00:06:19.600
And I'm also Chen Aming.

00:06:22.880 --> 00:06:24.760
From the past, to now,
and into the future,

00:06:26.840 --> 00:06:28.000
I'll always remember,

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:30.760
always.

00:06:32.440 --> 00:06:33.280
Aming.

00:06:34.160 --> 00:06:35.440
Everything I owed you.

00:06:37.320 --> 00:06:38.880
The youth we missed.

00:06:39.520 --> 00:06:40.480
The tears we shed.

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:42.200
Up until today,

00:06:42.440 --> 00:06:43.540
standing right before you...

00:06:46.160 --> 00:06:47.400
I've repaid them all.

00:06:50.920 --> 00:06:51.760
Ding Daang,

00:06:52.520 --> 00:06:53.360
tell me,

00:06:55.040 --> 00:06:56.120
is this what you wanted?

00:06:58.480 --> 00:06:59.320
Is it?

00:07:00.840 --> 00:07:02.200
Your one and only

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:04.360
Chen Aming.

00:07:05.480 --> 00:07:06.440
I did it.

00:07:12.640 --> 00:07:13.960
You never owed me anything.

00:07:16.760 --> 00:07:17.760
Thanks for waiting.

00:07:24.520 --> 00:07:25.360
Red.

00:07:26.720 --> 00:07:27.560
Same here.

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:35.040
No more pretending from now on.

00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:35.880
That feels great.

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:38.120
My dear Dr. Hu, thank you.

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:44.200
Showing off your love, huh?

00:07:48.520 --> 00:07:49.560
Sorry about that.

00:07:49.560 --> 00:07:50.480
Not as sweet as us.

00:07:54.520 --> 00:07:55.840
My silly little brother.

00:07:55.840 --> 00:07:57.200
Your turn to make a big move.

00:08:00.600 --> 00:08:01.560
Alright, alright.

00:08:01.880 --> 00:08:02.920
Stop teasing them.

00:08:03.160 --> 00:08:04.800
Look, Xibei's ears are turning red.

00:08:08.100 --> 00:08:10.780
(Warning)

00:08:29.740 --> 00:08:33.580
(Warning)

00:08:34.040 --> 00:08:34.880
What's wrong?

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:46.440
You want Chen Aming
to come back that badly?

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:54.120
His health just triggered an alert.

00:08:54.120 --> 00:08:55.040
Turn on the locator.

00:08:57.300 --> 00:08:57.740
(Warning)

00:08:57.740 --> 00:08:59.020
(Tong Sui Store, Aiye Town)

00:08:59.880 --> 00:09:00.880
They're here.

00:09:01.450 --> 00:09:02.320
How did this happen?

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:03.560
The system's been overridden.

00:09:03.700 --> 00:09:05.060
A hidden program's been implanted.

00:09:05.280 --> 00:09:06.400
Must be Yu Kun behind this.

00:09:06.760 --> 00:09:08.000
Open the surveillance first.

00:09:10.400 --> 00:09:11.240
Ding Daang.

00:09:11.560 --> 00:09:12.480
Do you know

00:09:12.480 --> 00:09:14.160
how I managed to stay alive?

00:09:15.520 --> 00:09:16.360
You guys

00:09:16.840 --> 00:09:19.920
all want that coward Chen Aming back.

00:09:20.840 --> 00:09:22.880
He only knows
how to run away from reality.

00:09:23.160 --> 00:09:24.840
A man crushed by his past.

00:09:25.000 --> 00:09:26.720
No, he's not!

00:09:26.720 --> 00:09:27.800
Without Yu Kun,

00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:28.920
he should've been gone.

00:09:29.880 --> 00:09:30.720
Let me tell you.

00:09:31.160 --> 00:09:33.240
It was me, Yu Kun, who took it all on.

00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:34.280
It was me!

00:09:34.920 --> 00:09:36.200
When you were at your lowest,

00:09:36.720 --> 00:09:38.760
when you needed help most,
he pushed you away.

00:09:39.880 --> 00:09:41.080
He has no right to come back?

00:09:41.560 --> 00:09:43.240
You pretended to be Aming.

00:09:43.240 --> 00:09:44.280
You liar.

00:09:44.280 --> 00:09:45.440
I didn't.

00:09:46.840 --> 00:09:47.920
From the very beginning,

00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:50.520
I've always been Yu Kun.

00:09:57.160 --> 00:09:58.040
Let's get going now.

00:09:58.040 --> 00:09:59.280
Maimai, there's no time.

00:09:59.280 --> 00:10:00.560
We're too far from the store.

00:10:01.160 --> 00:10:02.520
Yu Kun's out of his mind.

00:10:02.920 --> 00:10:04.720
He must have planned this way ahead.

00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:06.080
He's been acting all along.

00:10:06.880 --> 00:10:08.000
I'm worried if this goes on,

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:09.340
Ding Daang might really get hurt.

00:10:09.340 --> 00:10:10.640
And even the boss will die.

00:10:17.120 --> 00:10:18.160
Ding Daang.

00:10:18.760 --> 00:10:21.000
Have you ever actually loved Chen Aming?

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:23.960
Then why can't you tell the difference

00:10:23.960 --> 00:10:25.800
between him and me?

00:10:26.840 --> 00:10:28.080
I'm not Aming.

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:30.160
I'm nothing like Aming!

00:10:30.160 --> 00:10:31.360
I'm not!

00:10:43.640 --> 00:10:44.800
Without me,

00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:46.880
you would have died

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:48.120
in some forgotten corner.

00:10:48.440 --> 00:10:49.600
Zhou Haoran.

00:10:50.280 --> 00:10:51.920
Lin Xibei.

00:10:52.440 --> 00:10:56.760
You two ungrateful rats.

00:10:57.720 --> 00:10:59.520
Why did you betray me?

00:11:00.040 --> 00:11:01.480
Why?

00:11:01.760 --> 00:11:03.360
Why?

00:11:04.220 --> 00:11:05.080
Boss.

00:11:05.080 --> 00:11:06.120
She is Ding Daang.

00:11:06.120 --> 00:11:07.200
The woman you loved most.

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:09.480
Shut up!

00:11:11.640 --> 00:11:13.680
If everything in the past was fake,

00:11:14.520 --> 00:11:15.600
then just end me now.

00:11:17.080 --> 00:11:18.760
If everything we had was a lie,

00:11:18.760 --> 00:11:20.040
then just take me out of this!

00:11:45.980 --> 00:11:52.980
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

00:11:57.380 --> 00:12:04.740
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

00:12:09.180 --> 00:12:11.140
♪They say♪

00:12:11.540 --> 00:12:19.940
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

00:12:20.460 --> 00:12:23.420
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

00:12:23.660 --> 00:12:29.580
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

00:12:30.980 --> 00:12:36.740
♪I've already lost you♪

00:12:36.740 --> 00:12:42.220
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

00:12:42.500 --> 00:12:48.460
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

00:12:48.460 --> 00:12:53.260
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

00:12:54.340 --> 00:12:58.380
♪The past will always pass♪

00:12:58.700 --> 00:13:06.300
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

00:13:06.780 --> 00:13:10.020
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

00:13:10.580 --> 00:13:16.220
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

00:13:18.700 --> 00:13:22.220
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

00:13:22.220 --> 00:13:28.460
♪But sadly, it's not you♪